nodes.text: This Consular-class cruiser was used by the Galactic Republic and was in service to Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker and Senator Padmé Amidala to travel to the watery planet known as Dac in a effort to stop a civil war between the Mon Calamari and the Quarren after the assassination of King Yos Kolina

After the assassination of Yos Kolina, talks broke down between the Mon Calamari and Quarren which lead the Jedi Council to send Skywalker and Padmé onboard this ship to prevent a civil war. After conversing with the Calamarians and Quarren, Skywalker, Padmé, and Gial Ackbar swam to the surface and contacted the Jedi aboard this ship.

After war broke out between the two tribes the Jedi made an attempt to return to this ship, but it was rigged with explosives and was blown up by the Karkarodon Riff Tamson before they made it to the ship.
